title: Reece Jenkin, boys basketball coach at Colfax High School, dies after pancreatic cancer battle
tone: Feb. 28Reece Jenkin, the boys basketball coach at Colfax High School and a coach with the Hooptown Elite club program in Spokane, died on Friday morning after a battle with pancreatic cancer. He was 45.Jenkin was diagnosed on Dec. 11 with inoperable Stage 4 pancreatic cancer, which had already metastasized to his liver.
